posting_body: ['The Meadows of Coon Rapids Apartments is in a wonderful neighborhood with quiet streets.', 'Enjoy a community-centered neighborhood close to many local businesses and dining.', 'Our community is just blocks from Highway 10 and Highway 47, two miles from the Coon Rapids Riverdale Station & Platform, and only 20 minutes from Minneapolis.', 'Come visit us today and make The Meadows your choice for apartment living in Coon Rapids!', '-Playground', '-Large Closets', '-Clubhouse', '-Flex', 'Rent Payment', '-Leash Free Bark Park', '-On-Site Management', '-BBQ/Picnic Area', '-Washer/Dryer', '-View', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Controlled Entry', '-Hub automated package receiving', 'Call:', 'show contact info', '1770 121st Ave NW, Coon Rapids, MN 55448', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
